 the impact of Federal investment to promote economic prosperity and quality of life in rural communities in the United States; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s2204b–3/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s2204b–3/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs2204b%E2%80%933%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"using innovation to resolve local and regional challenges faced by rural communities.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Establishment","label":"b Establishment","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s2204b–3/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s2204b–3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs2204b%E2%80%933%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s2204b–3/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s2204b–3/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs2204b%E2%80%933%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"There is established a Council on Rural Community Innovation and Economic Development (referred to in this section as the “Council”).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s2204b–3/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s2204b–3/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs2204b%E2%80%933%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Council shall be the successor to the Interagency Task Force on Agriculture and Rural Prosperity established by Executive Order 13790.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effecti